   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Kirezi Coffee Processing and Marketing Project. Kirezi Coffee</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the science and practice of food, feed, and fiber production (including forestry, wildlife, fisheries, aquaculture and floriculture) and its relationships to natural resources, processing, marketing, distribution, utilization (including nutrition), and trade.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to support the science and practice of food, feed, and fiber production (including forestry, wildlife, fisheries, aquaculture and floriculture) and its relationships to natural resources, processing, marketing, distribution, utilization (including nutrition), and trade. In addition, this award Sector: Agriculture (Coffee production and processing) Beneficiaries: 125 members of Kirezi&apos;s coffee growers cooperative Summary: The project funds will be used to support Kirezi&apos;s capacity to grow and process high quality coffee. Specifically, funds will be used for: an environmentally sound coffee washing station, a storage facility and solar-power equipped office, and rehabilitation of drying tables; to purchase a truck and motorcycle, pulping machine and other equipment; establish a working capital fund for cherry purchases, and to provide various management, marketing, and agricultural trainings. Funds will also be used to support the hiring of technical staff as well as other administrative expenses.. Kirezi Coffee Processing and Marketing Project.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To generate rapid, sustained, and broad-based economic growth.</narrative>
  </description>
